{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfae Delve into the World of Absence of Light: Embark on an Epic Action RPG Adventure in Cloudia! \ud83d\udde1\ufe0f </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/ponte.gif?t=1738788686\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf1f Immerse yourself in the captivating realm of Absence of Light, set in the mesmerizing world of Cloudia! Prepare to be mesmerized by a medieval-inspired journey, where mystical treasures and powerful weapons await your discovery. Take control of a heroic character and forge your arsenal with diverse weapons, each possessing unique attributes to strategically unleash devastating attacks upon the forces of darkness that now rule the once-glorious Old Realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/GrandMaster.gif?t=1738788686\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udca5 Unleash the Power of Action RPG Gameplay: face challenging battles, and uncover hidden secrets in an immersive gaming experience that will keep you hooked for hours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/exercito.gif?t=1738788686\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udff0 Discover the Enchanting Realm of Cloudia: Traverse through the charming village area, interact with intriguing characters, and collect valuable items that will aid you in your quest to restore light to Cloudia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/slime.gif?t=1738788686\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2694\ufe0f Master Formidable Combos: Choose your weapons wisely and create powerful combinations to conquer the darkness and bring back the radiance to Cloudia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/lavini.gif?t=1738788686\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcdc Unravel the Prologue: The fate of Cloudia hangs in the balance, and only your courage can shatter the sinister grasp of the shadows. Are you ready to become a legend?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\ude80 Join the Gaming Community: Connect with fellow adventurers, share tips, and showcase your achievements in Cloudia. Get ready for epic battles and unforgettable moments!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Lord of Blood Vermillion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2536710/3ac30e9629a2993494cae8a0a78aef5af564e2c8.jpg"},{"name":"Lav'ini Tempest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2536710/f68efad15027d2e4c9e6eca8e56c0e8d847df699.jpg"},{"name":"Grand Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2536710/4066623c5d8d086559f54327e40b9970b2f7bf59.jpg"},{"name":"Abyssal Grotesque","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2536710/2fe30c0e2e751df115e91663c31a33c62296e5bd.jpg"},{"name":"Big Knight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2536710/77dda8b6bcd354d6cc0aecb37592d285f4557147.jpg"},{"name":"Giant Black Knight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2536710/76ec7f18f48b89f1cf173358c062b96e78615d4a.jpg"},{"name":"Labyrinth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2536710/62a7868e128ba4f451fd056229b58da52d04ba73.jpg"},{"name":"First Death","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/publ